<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>¿Cuánto me conoces? ❤️</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.css"/>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/canvas-confetti@1.6.0/dist/confetti.browser.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

<div id="quiz-container" class="container">

    <div class="quiz-shell-header">
        <span id="question-counter">1 / 8</span>
        <span>Mario Challenge</span>
    </div>
    <div id="progress-dots" class="progress-dots" aria-hidden="true"></div>

    <div id="question-card" class="card text-center">
        <div id="timer" class="timer-bar"></div>
        <div class="memory-chip">recuerdo bloqueado</div>
        <h4 id="question-text" class="fw-bold my-4" style="color: #590d22;"></h4>
        <div id="options-container" class="d-grid gap-2"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="feedback-screen" class="card text-center d-none">
        <div class="image-wrapper mb-3">
            <img id="feedback-image" src="" class="img-fluid shadow">
        </div>
        <p id="feedback-message" class="italic-love"></p>
        <button onclick="nextQuestion()" class="btn btn-danger rounded-pill px-4">Siguiente recuerdo ❤️</button>
    </div>

    <div id="transition-screen" class="card text-center d-none transition-glow">
        <h2 class="italic-love" style="font-size: 2.5rem;">Antes de seguir...</h2>
        <div class="py-4">
            <p class="lead fw-bold">Cierra los ojos y no los abras hasta que te lo diga.</p>
            <div class="heart-pulse">❤️</div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted small">Haz clic aquí abajo solo cuando estés lista y tengas los ojos cerrados.</p>
        <button onclick="showFinalProposal()" class="btn btn-heart">Ya los tengo cerrados 🙈</button>
    </div>

    <div id="final-screen" class="card text-center d-none">
        <div class="proposal-scene">
            <div class="photo-constellation" aria-hidden="true">
                <img src="/images/san-valentin.jpg" class="photo-card photo-one" alt="">
                <img src="/images/san-vicente-beso.jpg" class="photo-card photo-two" alt="">
                <img src="/images/atardecer-vacas.jpg" class="photo-card photo-three" alt="">
                <img src="/images/calma.jpg" class="photo-card photo-four" alt="">
                <img src="/images/flores-coche.jpg" class="photo-card photo-five" alt="">
                <img src="/images/helado.jpg" class="photo-card photo-six" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="proposal-content">
                <span class="proposal-kicker">último desbloqueo</span>
                <h1>¿Quieres ser mi novia oficialmente?</h1>
                <p>
                    No por una foto concreta, sino por todas las risas, los planes improvisados,
                    los viajes, los abrazos y las ganas que tengo de seguir sumando contigo.
                </p>
                <div class="promise-grid">
                    <span>más planes</span>
                    <span>más risas</span>
                    <span>más nosotros</span>
                </div>
                <div class="proposal-actions">
                    <button id="btn-si" class="btn btn-yes btn-lg px-4 fw-bold shadow">Sí, quiero ❤️</button>
                    <button id="btn-no" class="btn btn-no btn-lg px-4 shadow">Aún no</button>
                </div>
                <p id="no-message" class="no-message" aria-live="polite"></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</div>

<script src="/javascripts/script.js?v=4"></script>
</body>
</html>
